headline.print_headline: Neureuther Leads German One-Two in Last Slalom of 2014
headline.main: Neureuther Leads German One-Two in Last Slalom of 2014

lead_paragraph: Felix Neureuther became the most successful German skier in the men’s World Cup with his 10th career victory in a slalom in Madonna di Campiglio on Monday.
